<template>
  <iframeLoading :iframeUrl="iframeUrl"></iframeLoading>
</template>

<script>
  import iframeLoading from '@/components/common/iframeLoading'
  import {BasePath} from '@/utils/config.js';
  export default {
    name: "StructureDesign",
    data() {
      return {
        CUSTOMER: process.env.VUE_APP_CUSTOMER
      }
    },
    computed:{
      TrustID() {
        return this.$store.state.productInfo.trustId;
      },
      iframeUrl() {
        let CUSTOMER = this.CUSTOMER;
        return BasePath + 'quickdeal/simple.html#/StructureDesign/'+ this.TrustID + (CUSTOMER && CUSTOMER == 'xiaomi' ? '?editable=false': '')
      }
    },
    components: {
      iframeLoading
    },
  }
</script>
